    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have gained the ability to make your speech intelligible to any creature. As a Magic action, choose one or more creatures within 60 feet of you, up to a number equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of one creature). The chosen creatures can magically understand you, regardless of the language you speak, for 1 hour.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a Long Rest, unless you expend a spell slot to use it again.</p>",
